<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tickeron — Best for AI pattern recognition</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">StockHero — Best for no-code stock trading bots</span></li>
